OL,6,FFailures to properly prepare for a
OL,7,Fpandemic in the UK are expected to be
OL,8,Flaid bare on Thursday as the UK Covid-
OL,9,F19 Inquiry publishes its first report.
OL,11,FInquiry chair Baroness Heather Hallett
OL,12,Fwill report on how well the UK was
OL,13,Fable to face a deadly outbreak in the
OL,14,Frun up to 2020 when the Covid-19
OL,15,Fpandemic swept across Britain.
OL,17,FThe report is expected to highlight
OL,18,Fthe UK's focus on preparing for a flu
OL,19,Fpandemic instead of a coronavirus
OL,20,Fpandemic.
