OL,6,FFormer health secretaries Matt Hancock
OL,7,Fand Jeremy Hunt were put under the
OL,8,Fspotlight during oral evidence
OL,9,Fsessions, alongside former prime
OL,10,Fminister Lord Cameron and former
OL,11,Flevelling up secretary Michael Gove.
OL,13,FLord Cameron conceded it was a
OL,14,F"mistake" for his government to focus
OL,15,Ftoo heavily on preparations for
OL,16,Fcombating a wave of influenza rather
OL,17,Fthan a coronavirus-like pandemic.
