OL,6,FProfessor Liam Smeeth, director of the
OL,7,FLondon School of Hygiene and Tropical
OL,8,FMedicine (LSHTM), told the PA news
OL,9,Fagency: "The key lesson from the first
OL,10,FUK Covid Inquiry report is that if the
OL,11,FUK waits for the next pandemic to
OL,12,Femerge, it will be too late.
OL,14,F"The fight against pandemics is like
OL,15,Fcounter-terrorism, we must use similar
OL,16,Fapproaches such as gathering and
OL,17,Fsharing the best intelligence on
OL,18,Fglobal disease threats and joining
OL,19,Fforces to confront outbreaks before
OL,20,Fthey become pandemics.
